<bibRefCitation author="Ledoyer, M." box="[1160,1335,1769,1793]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" pagination="1041 - 1096" refId="ref27331" refString="Ledoyer, M. (1993) Cumacea (Crustacea) de la campagne EPOS 3 du RV Polarstern en mer de Weddell, Antarctique. Journal of Natural History, 27, 1041 - 1096." type="journal article" year="1993">Ledoyer (1993)</bibRefCitation>
